title: Intimamente Tango - Floraleda Sacchi & Maristtela Patuzzi
description:
The CD presents a tango by unusual characters, poetic and intimate - in which melancholy, hope and sensuality come together. The compositions of Astor Piazzola are repeated in the original arrangements and creative Floraleda and signed by Maristella who invent a new musical key to this music. All it played in between tradition and innovation, classic and jazz, between improvisation and world music.

Harp - Floraleda Sacchi

Violin - Maristella Patuzzi
